# Performance Checklist

## Lists

- `ListView.builder` / `SliverList.builder` for any list past ~20 items. Never spread into a Column.
- `AnimatedList` only when needed.
- For chat: `reverse: true` + `addAutomaticKeepAlives: false`.

## Images

- `cached_network_image` for every network image.
- Specify `width` and `height` to enable memory cache cap.
- Use `memCacheWidth` and `memCacheHeight` for thumbnails.

## Rebuilds

- `const` constructors wherever the analyzer suggests.
- Riverpod `select()` for fine-grained subscriptions.
- Scoped `Consumer` widgets to wrap only the rebuilding subtree.
- Profile with DevTools rebuild overlay on list-heavy screens.

## Layout

- Avoid `IntrinsicHeight` / `IntrinsicWidth` — O(n²) in tree depth.
- `LayoutBuilder` only when truly needed.

## Animations

- Animate `transform` + `opacity` only.
- Long animations: use `RepaintBoundary` to avoid re-painting siblings.

## Bundle

- Tree-shake unused icon fonts: `--tree-shake-icons`.
- Audit `flutter build apk --analyze-size` periodically.
- Defer heavy libs with deferred-import where possible.

## Network

- Debounce search inputs (300ms).
- Cache repository reads with TTL on cold-load.
- Realtime subscriptions disposed on screen leave.


